Extremely enjoying all the music being released nowadays in Pakistan throughout.
Pakistani's really have good taste of music and all these Pakistani drama ost's then platforms like VELO sound station , Coke studio, Nescafé basement, cornetto pop rock, Strepsils stereo and Pepsi battle of bands really making the bars rise each time. Also we hope upcoming movies would have good music too, until we don't appreciate or celebrate the singles of artists released independently by them enough.
